{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01UrGncXGVuJoFdzKEJkUmrK","type":"tool_result","content":"C:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\03072022-Use-DataStoreService-to-Create-Components.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\05172022-Migrate-Promise-Provider-Pattern.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\06232022-Host-Guidance-Migrate-to-Dependency-Synthesizer.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\08242022-Document-Storage-To-Store-Object-Handles.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\08302022-Telemetry-Tracking-For-Deprecated-Flows.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\08312023-Track-Container-Session-Crashes.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\10022022-Hoop-Design.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\10052022-Telemetry-Measuring-Active-Users.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20221114-Migrate-HostContext-to-loop-types.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20221201-Google-Docs-Component.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20221201-YouTube-Component.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20221202-Generic-Link-Unfurl-Component.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20221205-Migrate-IFluidHTMLView-to-HTMLViewable-HTMLView.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20221220-Support-Component-Multiview.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20230116-Copilot-Component.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20230119-Delay-Load-HostTelemetrySink.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/office-bohemia/docs/developer-guide/designs\\20230306-Provide-TelemetrySink-as-an-Injectable-Dependency.md\nC:/Users/yemishin/o